lass=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531022\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531022\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 22, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pqe1665702671325.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pqe1665702671325.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pqe1665702671325.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pqe1665702671325\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the default window properties for all Form components of the application.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"pqe1665702671325__topic_d144656e1_d144657e1_d144658e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pqe1665702671325__p_d144659e1_d144660e1_d144661e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">WINDOW</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">uwindow</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Properties</var>)</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pqe1665702671325__section_omx_4vc_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d627062e71\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Properties</var>—semi-colon delimited list of property-value pairs.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Window properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__1\">Physical Property Name</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__2\">Property</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">BackColor</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rwc1665702587483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rwc1665702587483.html\" title=\"Color to use as the background of the object.\">Background Color (BackColor)</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ForeColor</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rbp1665702587714.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rbp1665702587714.html\" title=\"Color to use as the foreground (usually the text color).\">Foreground Color (ForeColor)</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">CellHeight</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hwg1665702769717.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hwg1665702769717.html\" title=\"Window property that defines the size of the virtual grid used in the form layout, expressed as a percentage of Font0. The grid is used when defining the form dimensions and the size and position of objects in the form layout.\">Cell Height (CellHeight)</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">LineSpace</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mbl1665702769794.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mbl1665702769794.html\" title=\"Runtime Window property of a Uniface form, which specifies the number of pixels between vertically adjacent fields.\">Line Space (LineSpace)</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">BackImage</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"scc1665702611448.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/scc1665702611448.html\" title=\"Image used as background for the application window, form, or entity. This property can be set in ProcScript.\">Background Image (BackImage)</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">HAlign</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kmv1665702611521.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kmv1665702611521.html\" title=\"This property determines how the data (text or image) is aligned in the widget, entity, area frame, or window.\">Horizontal Alignment (Halign)</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">VAlign</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gvp1665702611605.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gvp1665702611605.html\" title=\"This property determines the vertical alignment of data (text or image) in the widget, entity, area frame, or window.\">Vertical Alignment ( Valign)</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Hscale</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dbd1665702611680.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dbd1665702611680.html\" title=\"This property determines how the image is horizontally scaled; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent).\">Horizontal Scaling ( Hscale)</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">VScale</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sup1665702611757.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sup1665702611757.html\" title=\"This property determines how the image is scaled vertically; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent).\">Vertical Scaling ( Vscale)</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">PreserveAspect</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqe1665702671325__table_w2872ab1b5b3b5_w2873ab1b5b3_w2874ab1b5_w2875ab1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yxe1665702611833.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yxe1665702611833.html\" title=\"Determines whether the aspect ratio of the image is preserved at all times. True (default) or False.\">Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect)</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"pqe1665702671325__table_d17579e1_d17580e1_d17581e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ila1665702671184.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ila1665702671184.html\" title=\"The [application] section of the initialization file enables you to set application-level defaults for a Windows desktop application.\">[application]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pqe1665702671325__section_zwl_yvc_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d627062e341\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Default properties defined here can be overridden by properties set declaratively and by\n        the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$windowproperties</span> ProcScript function. For more information, see\n          <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bch1665702773514.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bch1665702773514.html\" title=\"Set or return the current window properties of a Form instance.\">$windowproperties</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<div class=\"example\" id=\"pqe1665702671325__example_b44_zvc_xvb\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pqe1665702671325__p_d144674e1_d144675e1_d144676e1\">Setting the background color:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"pqe1665702671325__pre_c44_zvc_xvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[application]\nwindow=uwindow(backcolor=steelblue)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pqe1665702671325__p_d144677e1_d144678e1_d144679e1\">Setting the background image to a glyph:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"pqe1665702671325__pre_d44_zvc_xvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[application]\nwindow=uwindow(backimage=^I_OK)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pqe1665702671325__p_d144680e1_d144681e1_d144682e1\">Setting the background image to an image on the file\n        system:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"pqe1665702671325__pre_e44_zvc_xvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[application]\nwindow=uwindow(backimage=@flower.jpg)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"pqe1665702671325__note_f44_zvc_xvb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Although it is possible to specify an absolute path to\n        an image, it is preferable to specify a relative path using the <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zrt1665702757821.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zrt1665702757821.html\" title=\"Specifies the name of the directory where image files are stored. You can specify more than one directory by using a comma-separated list.\">Images</a> setting in the [paths] section.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pqe1665702671325__p_d144683e1_d144684e1_d144685e1\">Setting the background color and image, and the\n        alignment and scaling properties of the background image.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"pqe1665702671325__pre_g44_zvc_xvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">window=uwindow(backcolor=blanchedalmond;backimage=@blue_banner.jpg;valign=top;halign=left;hscale=100;vscale=100)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531022\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531022\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Window Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 22, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Set the default window properties for all Form components of the application. WINDOW = uwindow ( Properties ) Arguments Properties —semi-colon delimited list of property-value pairs. Table 1. Window properties Physical Property Name Property BackColor Background Color (BackColor) ForeColor Foreground Color (ForeColor) CellHeight Cell Height (CellHeight) LineSpace Line Space (LineSpace) BackImage Background Image (BackImage) HAlign Horizontal Alignment (Halign) VAlign Vertical Alignment ( Valign) Hscale Horizontal Scaling ( Hscale) VScale Vertical Scaling ( Vscale) PreserveAspect Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect) Default value: None File section: [application] Description Default properties defined here can be overridden by properties set declaratively and by the $windowproperties ProcScript function. For more information, see $windowproperties . Setting the background color: [application] window=uwindow(backcolor=steelblue) Copy Setting the background image to a glyph: [application] window=uwindow(backimage=^I_OK) Copy Setting the background image to an image on the file system: [application] window=uwindow(backimage=@flower.jpg) Copy Note: Although it is possible to specify an absolute path to an image, it is preferable to specify a relative path using the Images setting in the [paths] section. Setting the background color and image, and the alignment and scaling properties of the background image. window=uwindow(backcolor=blanchedalmond;backimage=@blue_banner.jpg;valign=top;halign=left;hscale=100;vscale=100) Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}